dataIdInfo.idAbs: The tax code layer is published every year normally during the spring through the Will County Clerk Tax Extension. This layer contains various annotation for any property within Will County. The tax map annotation entered is only digitized based upon plats and recorded documents received by the Tax Extension within the Will County Clerk Office.
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This polygon layer contains the municipal boundaries represented on the tax code layer built for the levy year.

Consts.useLimit: Under no circumstances may the data be redistributed or made available over a network without explicit permission from the Will County GIS Department. It is required that the Will County GIS Department be cited in any products generated from the data. The following source citation must be included: "Source: Levy Year Will County Municipalities" For custom requests a client must submit a written request stating the intended applications for the data to the Will County GIS Department. When the request is granted, data may be used only for the purposes explicitly stated in the written request.
